reviewText: Always had a love for this car and owned 2 of them in the 70's and watching this dvd brought back great memorys and anybody who watched this dvd could not help but want one of these great cars themselves

I bought this for my boyfriend who is working on restoring a 1969 GTO Judge. I think that he will enjoy it. Since it hasn't been opened yet, I can't really review the DVD itself but the packaging is fine and it arrived promptly.
